modules.description: Provides functions to load, parse, and query a Certificate Authority store from files or strings, supporting PEM and DER formats. Operates on byte sequences, file paths, and certificate collections. Used to validate TLS connections by checking peer certificates against a trusted store.

Provides access to the Mozilla CA certificate store in PEM format and a list of certificate strings suitable for use with X509 libraries. Operates on strings and lists of strings to represent certificates. Used to load trusted root certificates for secure TLS connections.
